OL,7,F"As soon as we were made aware of the
OL,8,Ffirst allegation, we took immediate
OL,9,Fand decisive action. The individual
OL,10,Fwas dismissed from their role with
OL,11,Fimmediate effect and we fully
OL,12,Fcooperated with the police
OL,13,Finvestigation at all times.
OL,15,F"This included providing the contact
OL,16,Fdetails of all customers who were
OL,17,Fbooked in with the individual. We were
OL,18,Fadvised by the Police not to make an
OL,19,Fannouncement regarding the allegations
